Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)
Functional Assessment of Chronic Illness Therapy - Palliative Care Questionnaire (FACIT-Pal)

extension.valueString:
define "Two Vaccine Regimen":
  [Immunization: Dash."HPV Immunization"] Vaccines
  where Vaccines.occurrence.value in Interval[Patient.birthDate + 9 years, Patient.birthDate + 15 years + 146 days]

define "Three Vaccine Regimen":
  [Immunization: Dash."HPV Immunization"] Vaccines
  where Vaccines.occurrence.value in Interval[Patient.birthDate + 15 years, Patient.birthDate + 45 years]

define "HPV Vaccinated":
  (Count("Two Vaccine Regimen") = 2 and "Two Vaccine Regimen"[1].occurrence >= "Two Vaccine Regimen"[0].occurrence + 146 days)
    or
  (Count("Three Vaccine Regimen") = 3 and "Dates Not Equal"("Three Vaccine Regimen"))

define "SDE HPV Vaccination Status":
  HPVVaccinationSDE."HPV Vaccinated"

define ColposcopyProcedures:
  C3F.Completed(
    [Procedure: "Colposcopy procedure"] union
    [Procedure: "Surgery Female Genital System Cervix Uteri"]
  )

define CervicalCytologyReports:
  Common.CompletedDiagnosticReport(
    Common.LookBack(
      [DiagnosticReport: "Pap Test"],
      CervicalCytologyLookbackPeriod
    )
  )

define "Abnormal Cytology":
  (ManagementLibrary.SortedCytologyReports Cytology
    where Cytology.date in Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 6 months, start of "Measurement Period" + 6 months)
      and Cytology.riskTableInput in {'ASC-H','AGC','HSIL+'})
  //The CQL code below will be removed once the SCC code is integrated into the CQL libraries.
  union
  ([DiagnosticReport: "SCC"] DR
    where DR.effective overlaps Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 6 months, start of "Measurement Period" + 6 months)
      and DR.code ~ "SCC")

define "Abnormal HrHPV":
  ManagementLibrary.SortedHpvReports HrHPV
  where HrHPV.date in Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 6 months, start of "Measurement Period" + 6 months)
    and HrHPV.riskTableInput in {'HPV16-, HPV18+', 'HPV16+'}
Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date

define "Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date":
  Last(("Abnormal Cytology" union "Abnormal HrHPV") tests
  return tests sort by date).date

// Look for treatments after this CIN2/CIN3 biopsy
define CervicalPrecancerTreatments:
  Dash.CervicalExcisionProcedures union
    Dash.CervicalAblationProcedures

define "Colposcopy or Treatment Referral":
  ([ServiceRequest: "Referral for Colposcopy"] ColpoReferral
    where ColpoReferral.status in { 'draft', 'active', 'on-hold', 'completed' }
    and ColpoReferral.doNotPerform is not true)
  union
  ([ServiceRequest: "Referral for Treatment"] TreatmentReferral
    where TreatmentReferral.status in { 'draft', 'active', 'on-hold', 'completed' }
    and TreatmentReferral.doNotPerform is not true)

define "Numerator":
  exists (Dash.ColposcopyProcedures C
    where Common.ProcedureDate(C) 6 months or less after "Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date")
  or
  exists (ManagementLibrary."SortedBiopsyReports" Biopsy
    where Biopsy.date 6 months or less after "Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date")
  or
  exists (ManagementLibrary."CervicalPrecancerTreatments" AblationOrExcision
    where Common.ProcedureDate(AblationOrExcision) 6 months or less after "Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date")
  or
  exists ("Colposcopy or Treatment Referral" R
    where R.authoredOn 30 days or less after "Last Abnormal Cervical Cancer Screening Result Date")

// Sex assigned at birth
define FemaleBirthSex:
  exists(
    Patient.extension E
      where E.url = 'http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-birthsex'
      and E.value = 'F'
  )

define GenderIdentity:
  Patient.extension E
    where E.url = 'http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/patient-genderIdentity'

define TransgenderMale:
  exists(
    GenderIdentity E
      where E.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept ~ "Transgender Male Code"
  )

define "Initial Population":
  AgeInYearsAt(date from start of "Measurement Period") in Interval[24, 65]
    and TLSL.FemaleorTransgenderMale
    and
      (exists "Abnormal Cytology"
      or exists "Abnormal HrHPV")

define "Has Hospice Services":
  exists (
    [Encounter: "Encounter Inpatient"] InpatientEncounter
			where InpatientEncounter.status = 'finished'
		    and (
	        InpatientEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition ~ "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)"
				    or InpatientEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition ~ "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)"
	    	)
				and InpatientEncounter.period ends during day of "Measurement Period"
	)
    or exists (
      [Encounter: "Hospice Encounter"] HospiceEncounter
        where HospiceEncounter.status = 'finished'
          and HospiceEncounter.period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists (
      ["Observation": "Hospice care [Minimum Data Set]"] HospiceAssessment
        where HospiceAssessment.value ~ "Yes (qualifier value)"
          and Global."Normalize Interval"(HospiceAssessment.effective) overlaps "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists (
      [ServiceRequest: "Hospice Care Ambulatory"] HospiceOrder
        where HospiceOrder.status in {'active', 'completed'}
          and HospiceOrder.intent = 'order'
          and Global."Normalize Interval"(HospiceOrder.authoredOn) during day of "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists (
      [Procedure: "Hospice Care Ambulatory"] HospicePerformed
        where HospicePerformed.status = 'completed'
          and Global."Normalize Interval"(HospicePerformed.performed) overlaps "Measurement Period"
    )

define "Normal Cytology":
  ManagementLibrary.SortedCytologyReports Cytology
  where Cytology.date in Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 6 months, start of "Measurement Period" + 6 months)
  and Cytology.riskTableInput = 'NILM'

define "Normal HrHPV":
  ManagementLibrary.SortedCytologyReports Cytology
  where Cytology.date in Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 6 months, start of "Measurement Period" + 6 months)
  and Cytology.riskTableInput = 'HPV-negative'
Palliative Care in the Measurement Period

define RemovalOfCervixProcedures:
  C3F.Completed(
    [Procedure: "Removal of Cervix Procedures"]
  )

define AbsenceOfCervixDiagnoses:
  [Condition: "Diagnosis of Absence of cervix"]

define AbsenceOfCervixObservations:
    C3F.Verified(
      [Observation: "Absence of cervix observation"]
    )

define AbsenceOrRemovalOfCervix:
  HasRemovalOfCervixProcedures or
  HasAbsenceOfCervixDiagnoses or
  HasAbsenceOfCervixObservations

define "Absence of Cervix":
  ManagementLibrary.AbsenceOrRemovalOfCervix
  or exists C3F.Completed(
    [Procedure: "Removal of Cervix Procedures CPT"]
  )

define "Denominator Exclusions":
  Hospice."Has Hospice Services"
  or Last("Normal Cytology").date > Last("Abnormal Cytology").date
  or Last("Normal HrHPV").date > Last("Abnormal HrHPV").date
  or PalliativeCare."Palliative Care in the Measurement Period"
  or ManagementLibrary."HasCervicalCancerDiagnoses"
  or "Absence of Cervix"
